<sup>
</sup> The Triangle Rewards Program is owned and operated by Canadian Tire Corporation, Limited. Triangle credit cards are issued by Canadian Tire Bank. Rewards are in the form of electronic Canadian Tire Money (CT Money). To collect bonus CT Money you must use your Triangle Rewards card or pay with a Triangle credit card at time of purchase. You cannot collect paper Canadian Tire Money on bonus offers. The bonus multiplier is based on the base rate of collecting CT Money (0.4%), and will be added to whatever the Member would otherwise collect, without the bonus. Example: On a $100 (pre-tax) purchase with a 20x bonus multiplier a Member would earn a bonus $8 in CT Money (20 X .4% X $100).
 Not all items sold at Canadian Tire are eligible to earn CT Money or to be redeemed for. Conditions apply. Visit <a href="http://click.myctm.canadiantire.ca/?qs=cf00275c32505c23b46edbce88798636d8e8d92d67aad2a3dd7880b8d9fdbfa953ee8f1cceefcf94a2b779949b32dee18b485e178d18187f" target="_blank" style="color:#515151; text-decoration: none;" ><u>triangle.com</u></a> for full program rules and Partner location information. No rainchecks on bonus CT Money. Only accounts selected for this promotion are eligible to participate.

            *25x
 Curbside Bonus CT Money offer is valid on purchases made online at Sport Chek & Atmosphere between Thursday, July 22- Monday July 26, 2021. Applies to applicable locations only. Orders not picked up within 2 weeks of purchase will be cancelled. Not valid on gift cards, tickets or sharpening cards. Excludes select brands & styles. No cash value. Bonus CT Money will be applied to the Member's Triangle Rewards Account 8 weeks after July 26, 2021.
  <br><br>
**Friends and Family offer is valid in-store and online from Thursday, July 22- Monday July 26, 2021. Online orders must be completed by 1:59am et by Tuesday July 27, 2021. No cash value. Excludes taxes and cannot be combined with any other 3rd party offer. The friends & family offer of take 25% off our ticket price excluding items already marked down and take 10% off our ticket price is on already reduced items is applicable to our ticket price on store merchandise. Excludes bikes, weights, heavy bags, Apple, Arcteryx, Bauer Elite/Performance, Birkenstock, Brooks, CCM Elite, Fitbit, Garmin, GoPro, Yeti & select Nike, Converse, marquee footwear ending in $.00 & other select brands &
 styles. Selection & availability may vary by location. Not valid on tickets, gift cards, previous purchases, custom orders, service shop services & shipping costs. Other exceptions may apply. Limit one coupon or online promo code per purchase. Coupon must be presented in-store at time of purchase. Promo code must be entered at time of online purchase. Other exceptions may apply. Friends & Family offer not valid at our Promenade, Thornhill, ON and Richmond Centre, Richmond, BC locations. Not valid in Atmosphere stores located in the province of Quebec or Whitehorse, YK.

  <br><br>
The Triangle Rewards Program is owned and operated by Canadian Tire Corporation, Limited. Triangle Mastercard, Triangle World Mastercard and Triangle World Elite Mastercard are issued by Canadian Tire Bank. Rewards are in the form of electronic Canadian Tire Money (CT Money). To collect bonus CT Money you must present a Triangle Rewards card/key fob, or use any approved Cardless method, at time of purchase or pay with a Triangle credit card. You cannot collect paper Canadian Tire Money on bonus offers. Any bonus multiplier is based on the base rate of collecting CT Money (0.4%), and will be added to whatever the Member would otherwise collect, without the bonus. Example: On a $100
 (pre-tax) purchase with a 20x bonus multiplier a Member would earn a bonus $8 in CT Money (20 X .4% X $100). Not all items sold are eligible to earn CT Money or to be redeemed for. Conditions apply. Visit <a href="http://click.myctm.canadiantire.ca/?qs=a3f200c665086477359b4b84f929f1deb227ce42da1bf98b018f6ff4b1639523f98f69b2f876729d241cd2e2b1e51db5da1248a504ace22f" target="_blank" style="color:#515151; text-decoration: none;" ><u>triangle.com</u>
</a> for full program rules and Partner location information. The offered rate is exclusive of any bonus or promotional offers or redemption transactions. CT Money is collected on the pre-tax amount of the purchase. The 20x Bonus Canadian Tire Money is valid for a one-time use and will be applied to the first qualifying online or in-store purchase made at the first qualifying retailer (Canadian Tire, Sport Chek, Atmosphere, Marks, Lquipeur, Party City and participating Sports Experts) after activating the offer. Online transactions must be fulfilled by the qualifying retailer during the offer period to qualify.  No rainchecks.  Offer must be activated. Only accounts selected are
 eligible.
